==English==

===Etymology===
From the game of [[w:Poker|Poker]], from the dishonest hiding of a high-value Ace card for use during play.

===Idiom===
'''[[ace]] [[up]] [[one]][['s]] [[sleeve]]'''

# {{idiom}} A surprise [[advantage]] of which others are not aware.

